Instructions:

-Press P to pause the simulation
-Right click or middle click and drag while auto camera focusing is disabled to move the camera
-Left click on a body while paused to remove it
-Left click in an empty area while paused to create a body
  -Boxes (in order): Mass, R, G, B, X velocity, Y velocity (These will also display if you hover over the boxes)
-Use scroll wheel to zoom in/out